translation.Message_0_Page_0: I'm not a fugitive! Okay, well I am. But you can't tell the military where I am. I can't go back there!
translation.Message_0_Page_1: My buddy and I managed to allude from law enforcement and the military. But they still need us for experimentation and so we don't expose any classified information.
translation.Message_0_Page_2: I have to find my friend and get out of here. Then we have got to meet up with our friend T. Rickster to give him a special cake to celebrate.
translation.Message_0_Page_3: We only can get to him however if our man on the inside is still there...
translation.Message_0_Page_4: Can you do me a quick favor?
translation.Message_1_Page_0: There's not much time. I'm on a strict schedule!
translation.Message_3_Page_0: Okay, thank you. Now I have to pull this off quick before I get caught and it's too late. If you see Lukas at the HQ tell him I'm ready.
translation.Response_1: Alright I'll see what I can do.
translation.Response_3: Hey, this is between us. Good luck.
translation.Response_4: I can't be apart of this. I have to go.
